NOTICE

This repository is a modified version of the upstream TOAD repository (Mahmood Lab),
which is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 (AGPL-3.0).

Major modifications introduced in this fork include:
- primary-site classification only (architecture/loss adapted)
- learning-curve runner for label fractions (x% training data)
- patient-level stratification enabled by default
- additional logging and reproducibility utilities
- containerized execution support
- release of pretrained weights and feature tensors used in the accompanying manuscript

See README.md, UPSTREAM.md, and CHANGES.md for details.
